org.perfidix.result

Class AbstractResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfidix.result.AbstractResult
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractResultContainer, MethodResult

    public abstract class AbstractResult
extends Object
    Results which are generated through the benchmark are stored in the inherted implementation of this class. The storage is done corresponding to the mapping of meters.
    Author:
    Sebastian Graf, University of Konstanz, Alexander Onea, neue Couch
